      "content": "counselors and advisors wont fix the fact that i'm a total failure. everyone looked up to me and now i'm just a joke. i look at my wife and my kids and i just feel like a burden. like, if they knew the real numbers, they'd hate me. it feels like the only way to actually stop the humiliation is to just not be around to face it anymore.",
